0.message: NEW EPISODE! It’s been a long, hot day in the desert, and Stella has just found a tranquil oasis. Finally, a well-deserved rest for our witch! Will it be a quiet night…or will the sneaky Morgana get up to her new tricks?

2.message: "We’re making some important changes in Witch Country. Make sure you update the game to the latest version on your mobile device to access all the bubblific new content!" - Violet
